# Task 007 Context Sync Report

## Task Overview

Task 007 (Gateway Online Message Delivery) is complete and approved. After
`MessageWsHandler::handle_send` persists a message successfully, the handler
now pushes a `CMD_PUSH_MESSAGE` + `im.push.PushRequest` protobuf to the
recipient's active WebSocket sessions via `ConnectionManager` and
`WebSocketServer`, and marks the message delivered after at least one
successful push. Push is best-effort: offline recipients stay undelivered
for later offline-pull.

